    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may spend a spell point as a standard action to gain a special sense that grants you a +1 bonus on Knowledge (nature) and Survival checks. This bonus increases by +1 every 5 caster levels. You may dismiss this sense at any time as an immediate action to reroll any failed Survival check avoiding natural hazards or getting lost, gaining a bonus to the roll equal to that granted by Nature Sense. This stacks with any class features with the same name.</p>\n",
